name: PHAssetResourceType
desc: Describes the relationship of an asset resource to its owning asset.

items.name: case photo
items.desc: Provides the original photo data for its asset.

items.name: case video
items.desc: Provides the original video data for its asset.

items.name: case audio
items.desc: Provides the original audio data for its asset.

items.name: case alternatePhoto
items.desc: Provides photo data that isnâ€™t the primary form of its asset.

items.name: case fullSizePhoto
items.desc: Provides a modified version of the original photo asset.

items.name: case fullSizeVideo
items.desc: Provides a modified version of the original video asset.

items.name: case adjustmentData
items.desc: Provides data for use in reconstructing recent edits to its asset.

items.name: case adjustmentBasePhoto
items.desc: Provides an unaltered version of its photo asset for use in for use in reconstructing recent edits.

items.name: case pairedVideo
items.desc: Provides the original video data component of a Live Photo asset.

items.name: case fullSizePairedVideo
items.desc: Provides the current video data component of a Live Photo asset.

items.name: case adjustmentBaseVideo
items.desc: Provides an unaltered version of its video asset.

items.name: case adjustmentBasePairedVideo
items.desc: Provides an unaltered version of the video data for a Live Photo asset for use in reconstructing recent edits.
